high_descs: Turn left, hang a right at the wall, head right at the counter ahead and walk to the sink on the left.
Pick up the green apple inside the sink on the left side.
Turn left and walk to the microwave on the counter ahead.
Put the apple inside the microwave to the left of the egg, heat it for a few seconds, remove it and close the door.
Turn left and hang a left at the cook top range to reach the counter with the stove.
Put the heated apple to the left of the clear container on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Place a heated apple on a counter.

high_descs: Turn left and walk to the wall, then turn right and walk across the room, then turn right and take two steps then turn left.
Pick up the green apple on the left side of the sink.
Turn left and walk to the counter.
Open the microwave, place the apple inside, then turn on the microwave for three seconds then open the door and take the apple.
Turn to the left and take two steps, then turn to the left.
Place the apple to the left of the glass bowl.
Head straight and go to the sink
Grab the apple out of the sink
Turn left and stop at the microwave
Heat the apple in the microwave and then take it out
Turn around and stop at the kitchen island
Put the apple on the counter
anns.task_desc: Putting an apple on the kitchen island
